\b Spare Parts Consumption - Architecture\b0\par
Complaint Management System\par
\par

\b 1. Purpose\b0\par
Spare Parts Consumption records spare parts used for a machine. It links Installed Base and optionally Service Log, and stores header details plus line items (part code, quantity, etc.).\par
\par

\b 2. Main Files\b0\par
\bullet  spare_parts_consumption.php - list, add/edit form, grid actions\par
\bullet  spare_parts_consumption_details.php - view one record\par
\bullet  delete_spare_parts_consumption.php - delete record\par
\bullet  includes/spare_parts_helpers.php - validation and save logic\par
\bullet  api/spare_parts_datatable.php - grid data\par
\bullet  api/spare_parts_get.php - edit data\par
\bullet  api/spare_parts_create.php - create and update\par
\par

\b 3. Shared Components\b0\par
\bullet  spare_parts_items.js / spare_parts_select2.js - line items and part search\par
\bullet  service_log_spare_parts_modal.php - add Spare Parts from Service Log\par
\bullet  api/installed_base_spare_parts_prefill.php - prefill from Installed Base\par
\bullet  api/service_log_spare_parts_prefill.php - prefill from Service Log\par
\bullet  rbac_access_helpers.php - permissions\par
\bullet  after_market_access_helpers.php - user record access\par
\par

\b 4. Basic Flow\b0\par
\bullet  User opens Spare Parts Consumption page\par
\bullet  Grid loads records from spare_parts_consumption table\par
\bullet  User adds or edits a record and links Installed Base / Service Log\par
\bullet  Line items are entered for parts used\par
\bullet  Header is saved to spare_parts_consumption\par
\bullet  Items are saved to spare_parts_consumption_items\par
\bullet  Also opened from Installed Base or Service Log grid actions\par
\par

\b 5. Database\b0\par
Main tables: spare_parts_consumption, spare_parts_consumption_items\par
Related tables: installed_base, service_logs\par
\par

\b 6. Permissions\b0\par
RBAC module: spare-parts-consumption (view, add, edit, delete)\par
}
